Package: glmertree
Title: Generalized Linear Mixed Model Trees
Date: 2016-07-30
Version: 0.1-1
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Marjolein", family = "Fokkema", role = "aut", email = "M.Fokkema@fsw.leidenuniv.nl"),
             person(given = "Achim", family = "Zeileis", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "Achim.Zeileis@R-project.org"))
Description: Recursive partitioning based on (generalized) linear mixed models (GLMMs)
  using lmer()/glmer() from lme4 and lmtree()/glmtree() from partykit.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0), lme4, partykit (>= 1.0-4)
Imports: Formula, graphics, stats, utils
Suggests: vcd
